                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-1350-18350511 t18350511-1350-punishment-193"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">GREEN—
<rs id="t18350511-1350-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
